  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Generous buffet breakfast served on the panoramic terrace round the pool with views across La Marinedda beach.</p>
<p>Dinner is buffet style or waiter served and can be taken in one of the 3 onsite restaurants, all of which enjoy views across the bay and serve a blend of Mediterranean and local cuisine. For a less formal evening guests can dine in the Pizzeria Basiricco with its delicious pizzas cooked in a wood fired oven.</p>
<p>There's a bar in the reception area and one beside the pool where they sometime have live music playing in the evening. There's also a small bar near the beach so you can enjoy a drink with fantastic sea views. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
