  <description><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px 0px 11px;">Hotel Marinedda Thalasso &amp; Spa is ideally located on a hillside and has superb views over the Asinara Gulf. It’s close to the pretty fishing village of Isola Rossa and the white-sand Marinedda beach, where umbrellas and parasols are available (payable locally). Enjoy a choice of two swimming pools, one is located in the main grounds and the other seawater pool is closer to the beach. The hotel has three bars, one in the hotel one by the pool and a small one at the beach so you can always stay refreshed.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 11px;">The rooms are decorated in a warm and elegant Mediterranean style and have a veranda with two deckchairs. The Elicrisio Wellness Centre is a perfect retreat for indulging in relaxation, with open-air thalassotherapy pools and a part-indoor heated seawater pool with hydro massage, along with two saunas and a Turkish bath. There is a choice of three restaurants serving traditional Sardinian cuisine, fresh seafood and a pizzeria for those less informal evenings. (Reservations and extra charges may be applicable).</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 11px;">Car hire is recommended for this hotel. Hotel Marinedda Thalasso &amp; Spa is approx. 1 hour 30 mins from Olbia or Alghero Airport.</p>]]></description>
