  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Pools &amp; Beaches</span></strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel has two pools to choose between, a freshwater pool in the main hotel area and a saltwater pool close to the beach. Both are equipped with sun loungers and parasols and bar service.</p>
<p>The hotel's a few hundred metres from the public beach La Marinedda. Take a stroll a bit further along and you'll find lots of lovely bays to explore. It's possible to rent sun loungers and parasols for the day for a local charge. At the beach there's a snack bar, washrooms and dressing rooms available. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Thalasso Spa</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Pamper yourself at the Elicrisio Wellness Centre where they have facilities like the heated thalasso pool with hydro massage, open air saltwater pools varying in temperature, a jacuzzi, thalasso therapy and massage treatment cabins, Turkis bath, two saunas and a relaxation area. It's the perfect way to relax while you're away. The spa service and treatments are payable locally. </span></p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Trekking routes</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Flood tennis courts</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Mini basketball</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Archery</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;"></span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Five-a-side football pitch</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Gym equipment with Technogym machinery</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Windsurfing surfing and diving courses (bookable and payable locally)</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;"></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><u>General</u><strong style="text-decoration-line: underline;"><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;"> Facilities</span></strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Free</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;"> WiFi in the rooms and common areas</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Parking (free private car park covered and unattended) </span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Free shuttle service (at scheduled times) to Isola Rossa</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Free pushchair hire (on request at time of booking)</span></li>
<li><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;">Charging station for electric vehicles</span><span style="margin: 0px; line-height: 107%; family: 'Calibri',sans-serif;"></span></li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Mini &amp; Junior Club</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotel offer free clubs for young guests aged 3 - 11. It runs six days per week between 24 May - 11 Sep from 9.30am - 1pm and 3.15pm - 6.30pm. The programme includes group lessons, sporting activities and an evening entertainment programme after dinner. These clubs an be booked locally.</p>]]></familyDescription>
