  <freeKidsDescription><![CDATA[<p>There is a Mini &amp; Junior club for children aged 8-11 years during the summer months (21 May-9 Sept) for 6 days a week. The timings are 9:30-13:00 and 15:30-18:30. </p>]]></freeKidsDescription>
