  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>195 rooms furnished in typical Mediterranean style, decorated with chestnut timbers and local stones visible on the external facade. All room typologies have a large veranda with two deck chairs (or two chairs and a small table), bathroom with shower, hair dryer, air conditioning, telephone, TV, safe, minibar, bathrobes for adults and beach towels. They are decorated in an elegant way that expresses the islands simplicity with chestnut wood beams, wrought iron fittings and hand crafted works of art.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>sleep up to two adults and one child (aged 0 - 11). The rooms have a double bed (twin beds are available on request) and an extra bed can be added for a child. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>have a queen size bed.</p>
<p><strong>Relax Rooms</strong> are slightly larger and sleep up to two adults and one child (aged 0-11). They're light and airy with a double bed and single sofa bed or a built in sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>sleep up to 2 adults, one child (aged0 0-13) and one infant (aged 0-1). These rooms have a double bed and open plan lounge area with a sofa bed. </p>
<p><strong>Suite </strong>sleep up to two adults and two children (aged 0-13) and a fifth bed for a child is available on request.  They have a double bed and separate lounge area with a pull out or built in sofa bed for two people. </p>
<p><strong>Family Suites </strong>sleep up to four adults and a fifth bed for a child is available on request. They're made up of two interconnecting classic rooms. </p>
<p><strong>Senior Suite Family </strong>sleep up to four adults and two children (aged 0-13). They're made up of an interconnecting suite and classic room. </p>
<p><strong>President Sea View </strong>sleep up to two adults and two children (aged 0-13). These luxurious rooms have a large veranda with beautiful sea views over the bay. </p>
<p><strong>Executive Elicriso Sea View </strong>sleep up to two adults. </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
